A financial information service that provides a real-time visual display of the buy (bid) and sell (ask) orders currently open on [[MtGox]] exchange.

This service was first seen in May, 2011 but first appeared in the forum on June 11, 2011 (1.1).

The page requires a browser that supports Websockets.  Apple's Safari and Google's Chrome are two such browsers that support Websockets. 

